data.description: Amazing opportunity ready to move in 3 BR Condo not found elsewhere in the Metro.  Save hundreds of dollars a year with one of the lowest HOA dues around that includes more than just snow & lawn care – it covers highspeed Internet (1GB), Water-Sewer, Trash, Clubhouse, Pool, Theater room, Conference room, Common space cleaning repairs, etc.   Upgraded SS appliances, the living room with vaulted ceilings provides a spacious feel; has a gas fireplace w/large window for excellent natural light; & opens to a covered deck area w/ additional storage.  The large master bedroom & huge walk-in closet.  The 2 spare bedroom has balcony access (covered deck) perfect for a home office.  The 2 garage stalls provide covered parking & extra storage (parking space + extra space).  The perfect location is walking distance to Providence Pointe Park & Johnston High School. Easy access to retail, grocery, dining, & the Interstate.  Secure FOB access & 2nd story living provides excellent security.
